title: MP News: Supreme Court Quashes Charges Under SC/ST Act Against VYAPAM Whistleblower
description: The Supreme Court on Tuesday quashed SC/ST Act charges against Anand Rai, a whistleblower in the Madhya Pradesh VYAPAM scam. The case arose from alleged violence and abuse during a 2022 rally in Ratlam. The bench held the action was not in accordance with law. Rai had previously been granted bail, and trial proceedings under the Act were stayed.
